<section id="text-32" class="widget widget_text"><div class="widget-wrap"><h4 class="widget-title widgettitle">Insulin Resistance Challenge</h4>
			<div class="textwidget"><p>8-Week Program</p>

<center><a href="https://spotebi.com/workout-plans/free-fitness-challenge/"><img src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=&#039;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#039;%20width=&#039;500&#039;%20height=&#039;500&#039;%20viewBox=&#039;0%200%20500%20500&#039;%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt width="500" height="500" class="perfmatters-lazy" data-src="https://spotebi.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/insulin-resistance-fitness-challenge-spotebi-500x500.jpg" /></a></center>
<div class="small-break"></div>

<div class="homepage-subtitles"><p>Struggling with metabolic health and low energy? Our <b>8-Week Insulin Resistance Challenge</b> uses strength training, Norwegian-style cardio, and simple lifestyle habits to restore energy, improve metabolic health, and support a stronger heart!</p></div>

<div class="break"></div>
<center><a href="https://spotebi.com/workout-plans/free-fitness-challenge/"><div class="button">JOIN US!</div></a></center></div>
		</div></section>
